Period of messing from:&nbsp;<strong>15</strong></span><strong><sup><span style="font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
color:black;background:white;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">th</span></sup></strong><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">
 October 2016 to 25</span></strong><strong><sup><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;
background:white;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">th</span></sup></strong><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">
 November 2016.</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:
&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">The preferences registered last month and any time prior to 29<sup>th</sup> September 11am will be
<span name="searchHitInReadingPane" id="0.8864462129828012"><span class="currenthithighlight">erased</span></span> and you need to freshly register your preferences.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
color:black;background:white;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"><br>
<strong>Students who are facing technical problems in login&nbsp;may please fill the form by selecting the link given in the homepage.</strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:
normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">PLEASE NOTE:</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:
normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"><br>
<strong>Only after filling in the mess feedback form and updating your personal details, you will be able to do mess registration.
</strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:
normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:
normal">
<strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">If you want to change your name, Hostel Name, Room number etc,. Please submit your concern
 in link Help Desk</span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;<br>
The residents of Sarayu, Sharavati, Sharavati Ext. (Tunga) and Sabarmati hostels MUST choose one of the options
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"><br>
I prefer&nbsp;Vindhya / Mandakini only&nbsp;<em>(or)</em></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"><br>
<em>&nbsp;</em><br>
I&nbsp;prefer Himalaya and Vindhya / Mandakini</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<em><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">If they choose &#8220;</span></em><span style="font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
color:black;background:white;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">I
 prefer&nbsp;Vindhya / Mandakini only&#8221; then t<em>hey must choose any <strong>3 options out of 4</strong></em></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<em><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">.
</span></em><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
color:black;background:white;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"><br>
<em>And if they choose &#8220;</em>I&nbsp;prefer Himalaya and Vindhya / Mandakini&#8221; then they
<em>must choose any <strong>10 options out of 12 </strong></em>messes listed in the preference for messes in the portal.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">The male residents MUST give their preferences for a minimum of
<strong>8 out of 10</strong> messes listed in the preference for messes in the portal.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"><br>
Please note:</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"><br>
<strong>All the unregistered residents, both male and female, will be allocated to the messes that have vacancies and in this regard the decision of the Hostel Mess Allocation committee is final. No change of mess after allocation is entertained.
</strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">The allotment of girl students to Himalaya messes will be subject to availability.</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">Those who wish to dine in
</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">group<span style="background:white">s will have to do the following:</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"><br>
<br>
(a) There will be an option to create a unique </span><span style="font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">group<span style="background:white"> name.&nbsp; Please make
 sure the members of your </span>group<span style="background:white"> know the </span>
group<span style="background:white"> name (for example, if you type the </span>group<span style="background:white"> name as 'abc1' then make sure your
</span>group<span style="background:white"> members know that this is the </span>
group<span style="background:white"> name). Whoever creates the </span>group<span style="background:white"> name is the leader of the
</span>group<span style="background:white"> and the preferences given by that leader only will be used for allocation. If you are already a leader of a
</span>group<span style="background:white">, you cannot join another </span>group<span style="background:white"> or you cannot come out of the
</span>group<span style="background:white">.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">(b) There will be an option for joining a
</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">group<span style="background:white"> as member. You will be asked to type the
</span>group<span style="background:white"> name that you wish to join.&nbsp; One student can join in only one
</span>group<span style="background:white">. The members can opt out of the </span>
group<span style="background:white"> if they wish; they can also join another </span>
group<span style="background:white"> or register as individual at any time before the dead line for
</span>registration<span style="background:white">.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"><br>
<br>
(c) A </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:
EN-GB">group<span style="background:white"> can have a maximum of 8 members only.&nbsp; When the number in the
</span>group<span style="background:white"> exceeds 8, there will be a flag shown alerting that you cannot join that
</span>group<span style="background:white">.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"><br>
(d) Each </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:
EN-GB">group<span style="background:white"> will get only one chance in the random pick.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:
justify;line-height:normal">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white;
mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">Any additional decisions on mess allocation will rest with the Hostel Mess Allocation committee.
 Send you email to: <a href="mailto:ccw@iitm.ac.in" target="_blank"><span style="color:blue">ccw@iitm.ac.in</span></a></span></p>
